55) Develop a PHP script that uses stack functions to reverse a string.
<?php
function reverseString($str) {
$stack = str_split($str); // Convert string to array of characters
$reversed = "";
while (!empty($stack)) {
$reversed .= array_pop($stack); // Pop last character
}
return $reversed;
}
echo "Original: Hello<br>";
echo "Reversed: " . reverseString("Hello");
?>
Output:
Original: Hello
Reversed: olleH
